&lt;p&gt;Are you a great communicator with a passion for helping people?&lt;br&gt;Join a team where you can make a real impact by keeping customers connected to a product they love. At MyHeritage, we’re looking for driven and empathetic individuals to join our Retention team and help our global customers continue their journey of family discovery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Retention Representative, your primary role is to engage with paying customers who have requested a refund for their annual subscriptions, understand their concerns, and offer tailored solutions to retain them as valued members. Additionally, you will be responsible for promoting long-term subscription options that meet our customers’ needs.&lt;/p&gt;
